### 5.6 "Proven in Testing" Section

Title: "5 attack scenarios. All detected."

Show a timeline/table of the 5 scenarios:

```
Scenario | Attack Type              | Expected     | Result      | On-chain Pause
---------|--------------------------|--------------|-------------|---------------
    1    | Normal deposits + 3.3%   | No alert     | ✅ Silent   | N/A
         | withdrawal               |              |             |
    2    | Rapid 81% drain in       | TVL_VELOCITY | ✅ Severity | Confirmed
         | 3 transactions           | fires        | 99, <3s     | 3sX4PLsG...
    3    | Flash loan + 40%         | FLASH_LOAN   | ✅ Severity | Confirmed
         | drain exploit            | _DRAIN fires | 64, <5s     | 28wPiUda...
    4    | 10% single drain         | No alert     | ✅ Silent   | N/A
         | (below threshold)        |              |             |
    5    | Slow 5%×8 cumulative     | TVL_VELOCITY | ✅ Fires at | Cooldown
         | bleed                    | fires ~s5    | slice 5     | active
```

Style this as a clean table with green checkmarks, red borders on attack rows,
and monospace font for the transaction signatures.

