### 7.5 Alert History Table (full width)

Columns:
```
Alert ID | Rule | Severity | At Risk | Slot | Time | On-chain Tx | Status
```

- Alert ID: first 8 chars, monospace, click to open modal
- Rule: RuleBadge component
- Severity: SeverityBar (0-100 visual) + number
- At Risk: formatUSD
- Slot: monospace #XXXX
- Time: timeAgo
- On-chain Tx: ExplorerLink or "—" if null
- Status: green MONITORED or red PAUSED

Pagination: 10 per page. Sort by created_at DESC default.
Click any row → AlertModal opens.

