Rule explanations sidebar (right 280px, collapsible):
```
Detection Rules Reference

R1 · Flash Loan + Drain
Fires when flash loan evidence (confidence > 50%)
is found within the same 10-slot window as a TVL
drop exceeding 20%. Score is weighted by confidence
and slot distance between flash and drain.

R2 · TVL Velocity
Fires when TVL drops more than 20% within a 10-slot
rolling window. Score scales linearly: 20%=60,
50%=80, 80%=99. Immune to false positives from
normal deposit/withdrawal cycles.

R3 · Bridge Outflow Spike
Fires when token outflows through known Solana bridge
programs exceed a configurable multiplier of the
30-slot average outflow baseline.
```

